# 🛡️ Telemetry Ingestion & Trust Flow

The **PoWV Protocol** transforms trusted industrial telemetry into independently verifiable digital evidence through a layered trust architecture.

```text
 Edge Device
      │
      ▼
 Secure Gateway
      │
      ▼
 Verification Layer
      │
      ▼
 Evidence Registry
```

```mermaid
flowchart LR

A[Edge Device]
--> B[Secure Gateway]

B
--> C[Verification Layer]

C
--> D[Evidence Registry]
```

## Components

| Layer | Purpose |
|--------|---------|
| **Edge Device** | Captures trusted industrial telemetry. |
| **Secure Gateway** | Validates and processes incoming events. |
| **Verification Layer** | Generates verifiable digital evidence. |
| **Evidence Registry** | Preserves immutable records for auditing. |

## Design Principles

- 🔒 Hardware-Assisted Trust
- 📡 Verifiable Telemetry
- ⚡ Cryptographic Integrity
- 🛡️ Tamper-Evident Evidence
- 🚂 End-to-End Traceability
- 🔌 Modular & Vendor-Neutral Architecture

> [!NOTE]
> This repository contains the **public research implementation** of the **PoWV Protocol**.
>
